# $Id: mkpasswd 570 2006-04-27 21:52:26Z michael $
MKPASSWD <plaintext> [DES|MD5]

The MKPASSWD command is essentially the same as the mkpasswd binary
distributed with hybrid. It can make an encrypted password for use
in the ircd.conf using either DES or MD5 encryption, and then give
you the salted result via NOTICE.
